snippet.title: Drawing a scene in Trouble Hunter Chronicles
snippet.description:
A sped up video of our artist making a scene from scratch for our upcoming point and click adventure game Trouble Hunter chronicles!

Do you like the art? Do you enjoy adventure games? Find out more about the game and let us know: https://discord.gg/MRxSrzc
